        public static java.lang.String prettyTimeSpan(double nanoTime)
        Converts the given nano time to an human readable string. for example prettyTimeSpan(n) = 5 hours, 2 minutes, 3 seconds
        Parameters:
        nanoTime - The time to convert
        Returns:
        The time string.

      • prettyTimeSpan

        public static java.lang.String prettyTimeSpan(double nanoTime,
                                              boolean showSeconds)
        Converts the given nano time to an human readable string. for example prettyTimeSpan(n) = 5 hours, 2 minutes, 3 seconds
        Parameters:
        nanoTime - The time to convert
        showSeconds - if set to true, round to seconds. if set to false, round to minutes
        Returns:
        The time string.
